STATE of Carolina
v.
Webster WALLER No. 253P18 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 20, 2018. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Michael D. Waters, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Webster Waller, for Waller, Webster.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 10th of August 2018 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 20th of September 2018."
